      "rationale": "In-vitro experiments used bovine blood at 33% hematocrit, viscosity 3.2 cP, matching CFD fluid properties. Flow rates controlled to ±0.05 L/min and rotational speed to ±10 RPM. Five operating points span the clinical CPB envelope. Test conditions are well-documented and boundary condition equivalence is confirmed. Required level 2 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
