      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under CPB operating conditions (3–6 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM) that span the intended clinical envelope. Fluid properties match clinical CPB circuit conditions. Geometric fidelity between validation and COU model confirmed by dimensional inspection report. Required level 2 achieved."
