      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published benchmarks for rotating internal flows. Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger correlation, alpha = 0.765, beta = 0.62) adopted from peer-reviewed literature. Model form sensitivity to turbulence model assessed by comparison with realizable k-epsilon; RH differed by 6.8%. Model form uncertainty acknowledged and bounded. Required level 2 achieved."
    },
