      "rationale": "Geometry from FDA-published CAD file (version 1.4). Boundary conditions derived from clinical CPB literature and matched to in-vitro test conditions. Fluid properties (density 1050 kg/m3, viscosity 3.2 cP) documented. Hemolysis model coefficients alpha = 0.765 and beta = 0.62 sourced from Giersiepen et al. (1990). Input uncertainty ranges documented in the model report. Note: while alpha is documented as a model input in the report narrative, it is not formally registered as a pinned deployment configuration parameter — a deployment analyst could substitute an alternative published value without triggering a re-validation review. Required level 2 achieved."
    },
